tables.setting:
CREATE TABLE `:table_prefix_setting` (
  `setting_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `action_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `value_text` text NOT NULL COMMENT 'json_encoded',
  PRIMARY KEY (`setting_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
tables.setting_action:
CREATE TABLE `:table_prefix_setting_action` (
  `action_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `module_name` varchar(32) NOT NULL,
  `action_group` varchar(32) DEFAULT NULL,
  `action_name` varchar(32) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`action_id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `action_group` (`action_group`,`action_name`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
